task.summary: Added a Vaadin project to visualize the sampled data
Added support for the arp command on macOS
Fixed arp command for macOS and improved the detection of the "reachability" folder
Refactored the LanSample class to traverse the file line by line(moe memory efficient) and to only parse the file when needed
Added javadoc to the LanSample class
Added a Grid view that shows all lan clients from the selected sample
Added a Jetty run configuration to allow on-line class reloading without restarting the pplication server every time
Added the LanClientsCore project to avoid code duplication
Added a service to manage whitelisted clients
